['Lad gayi lad gayi lad gayi', '
Bichhu buti o meri maa meri maa', '
Meri maa ui ui', '

Bichhu buti o meri ma meri maa', '
Meri maa ui ui', 'Jaa jaa jaa jalan badhti jaye', '

Jiya mora ghabraye haye rama', '

Bichhu buti o meri ma meri maa', '
Meri maa ui ui', 'Are haye mari haye mari haye mari', '

Ye chor chochra', '
Are khujlaye bin bat bane na', '
Aag lage man mora', '
Are khujlaye bin bat bane na', '
Aag lage man mora', '
Lad gayi lad gayi lad gayi', '
Bichhu buti o meri maa meri maa', '
Meri maa ui ui.']
